tment\n- Myeloid compartments (Monocytes, Dendritic cells) contract\n- Upregulated effector genes: GZMB, PRF1, IFNG, NKG7, GNLY\n- Downregulated genes suggest reduced monocyte/macrophage activity\n\n## Journal specs\n- Target: **Cell** (Elsevier)\n- Size: {FIG_WIDTH} in × {FIG_HEIGHT} in (double column)\n- Format: PDF (vector) + PNG (300 DPI) + grayscale preview\n- Color: Okabe-Ito colorblind-safe palette\n- Font: Helvetica/Arial, 7-8 pt\n- Panel labels: (A)(B) bold, Cell/Elsevier style\n\"\"\")\n\nprint(f\"\\n[✓] Figure 2 exported. Files saved to figs/fig2_scRNAseq.*\")\nprint(f\"    Description: {desc_path}\")\nprint(f\"    Total DEGs: {df_sig['direction'].value_counts().to_dict()}\")\n"})
